OL,3,CAsh Sarkar: 'The right might be
OL,4,Cwinning but the left is not doomed'
OL,6,FSelf-described communist Ash Sarkar
OL,7,Fhas insisted the UK's left-wing
OL,8,Fmovement is not doomed, despite the
OL,9,Frise of Nigel Farage, Reform UK and a
OL,10,Fglobal shift to the right.
OL,12,F"Nah, nah, nah, nah," the political
OL,13,Fcommentator says when asked. "We're in
OL,14,Fa bad place right now, but things
OL,15,Fchange quickly and they move quickly."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
