OL,3,CAsh Sarkar: 'The right might be
OL,4,Cwinning but the left is not doomed'
OL,6,FBut Sarkar, who has written a book
OL,7,Fanalysing where the left has gone
OL,8,Fwrong, admits she - and other
OL,9,Fpolitical commentators like her - may
OL,10,Fhave been part of the problem in
OL,11,Frecent years.
OL,13,FHer book, 'Minority Rule: Adventures
OL,14,Fin the Culture War', suggests
OL,15,Fintolerance on the left has alienated
OL,16,Fthe UK's working-class majority,
OL,17,Fallowing the likes of Farage to offer
OL,18,Fthem an alternative.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
