OL,3,CAsh Sarkar: 'The right might be
OL,4,Cwinning but the left is not doomed'
OL,6,FIt's created a culture war, the
OL,7,Fjournalist claims, where minorities
OL,8,Fare pitted against one another. But on
OL,9,Fnumerous occasions she's contributed
OL,10,Fto those wars with social media posts
OL,11,For TV appearances.
OL,13,F"There are certain things that I did
OL,14,Fin the past that I wouldn't do now,"
OL,15,Fshe says, looking back on times she'd
OL,16,Fbeen booked to speak on programmes
OL,17,Fabout issues facing Asian people.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
