OL,3,CAsh Sarkar: 'The right might be
OL,4,Cwinning but the left is not doomed'
OL,6,F"I was being used by a system of
OL,7,Fproducers and editors who were
OL,8,Fscripting the conversation before I'd
OL,9,Feven opened my mouth. And now that I'm
OL,10,Fbigger, older, and uglier, I'm happier
OL,11,Fsaying no to that kind of thing."
OL,13,FWatch the full interview here:
OL,15,FShe says culture wars have led to
OL,16,Fpeople blaming minorities - such as
OL,17,Fasylum seekers or trans people - for
OL,18,Fthe UK's problems, rather than
OL,19,Flandlords, media barons, hedge fund
OL,20,Fmanagers, and CEOs who she claims are
OL,21,Fthe real cause.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
