OL,3,CAsh Sarkar: 'The right might be
OL,4,Cwinning but the left is not doomed'
OL,6,F"The real villains in society aren't
OL,7,Ftrans people or people on the left who
OL,8,Fare maybe a bit oversensitive. It's
OL,9,Fpeople like Jeff Bezos and Elon Musk
OL,10,Fand Mark Zuckerberg," she tells me.
OL,12,FThe contributing editor for Novara
OL,13,FMedia accepts there are many reasons
OL,14,Ffor people to be angry in the UK, such
OL,15,Fas the tough housing market, but
OL,16,Fblames Prime Minister Keir Starmer for
OL,17,Fallowing them to be upset with the
OL,18,Fwrong groups.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
