OL,3,CAsh Sarkar: 'The right might be
OL,4,Cwinning but the left is not doomed'
OL,6,FShe says Labour is unable to "tap into
OL,7,Fthat anger" because it is "too busy
OL,8,Ftrying to pole dance" for huge
OL,9,Fcompanies by seeking their investments
OL,10,Frather than hitting them with new
OL,11,Ftaxes.
OL,13,FSarkar judges this has left Labour in
OL,14,Fa "very, very bad space right now.
OL,15,FThere isn't a political force for the
OL,16,Fleft which is tapping into people's
OL,17,Fanger. That anger is crying out for a
OL,18,Fpolitical expression that's not
OL,19,FReform".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
