OL,3,CAsh Sarkar: 'The right might be
OL,4,Cwinning but the left is not doomed'
OL,6,FThe "one way out" for Starmer, she
OL,7,Fsays, would be "to say we're going to
OL,8,Ftax wealth, we're going to deal with
OL,9,Fredistribution".
OL,11,FBut, hinting at Labour's small vote
OL,12,Fshare, she had a warning for the PM.
OL,14,F"Just because you've got a lot of MPs
OL,15,Fdoesn't mean you've actually got a lot
OL,16,Fof support in the country. Again,
OL,17,Fdangerous place for Labour to be
OL,18,Fsitting on top of the sand sandcastle
OL,19,Fmajority."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
