OL,3,CAsh Sarkar: 'The right might be
OL,4,Cwinning but the left is not doomed'
OL,6,FThe author does not support Labour
OL,7,Fsince Jeremy Corbyn's resignation
OL,8,Fbecause she does not see it as left-
OL,9,Fwing enough. And, despite voting Green
OL,10,Fat the last election, does not think
OL,11,Fthe party is capable of winning an
OL,12,Felection just yet.
OL,14,FSo, does she think this all means the
OL,15,Fleft-wing movement is doomed for a
OL,16,Fgeneration?
OL,18,F"Nah nah nah. I think that we're in a
OL,19,Fbad place right now," she says, "but
OL,20,Fthings change quickly and they move
OL,21,Fquickly.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
