OL,3,CAsh Sarkar: 'The right might be
OL,4,Cwinning but the left is not doomed'
OL,6,F"What I think the electoral left is
OL,7,Ffacing is not a crisis of
OL,8,Forganisation, because there are so
OL,9,Fmany organisations that sprang up
OL,10,Faround Corbynism as a crisis of
OL,11,Fleadership.
OL,13,F"They're looking for the right leader.
OL,14,FNow, I think it's probably got to be a
OL,15,Fwhite dude with a regional accent.
OL,17,F"I don't know who it's going to be,
OL,18,Fbut I think that's going to have to be
OL,19,Fthe set of identity characteristics,
OL,20,Fembodied by the leader."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
