OL,6,FShe added: "What Reform show is that
OL,7,Fthere is plenty of appetite for
OL,8,Fpolitical parties outside of the two
OL,9,Fparty duopoly.
OL,11,F"Now the right are doing it with
OL,12,FReform. Can the left do it with
OL,13,Fanother party? Maybe."
